01:40:17.291 --> 01:40:20.416
Unique design of the
door you’ll find here

01:40:20.583 --> 01:40:23.791
The unique door on the west Will
lead you to a secret passageway

01:40:24.125 --> 01:40:27.291
Move past the number of rooms
You’d counted earlier in the day”

01:40:27.958 --> 01:40:31.166
What does this even mean?

01:40:57.125 --> 01:41:05.583
I’ve tolerated a lot of injustice
and disrespect Through the years…

01:41:09.250 --> 01:41:12.125
But today Sakhhi Gopal
will talk the witness stand.

01:41:13.500 --> 01:41:14.875
You’ll reach the town’s north-east corner Covered
in dust, the founding father sleeps under the stair

01:41:16.500 --> 01:41:19.666
Let me see… This is straight
out of the Arabian Nights.

01:41:20.458 --> 01:41:21.166
What next?

01:41:21.583 --> 01:41:23.583
We have to cross this tunnel

01:41:23.666 --> 01:41:24.416
and come here.

01:41:24.583 --> 01:41:26.541
-I’m very sure the object is here…
-Right but…

01:42:30.708 --> 01:42:35.541
Your father’s deeds… I feel
bad about sharing them with you.

01:42:38.125 --> 01:42:40.083
But today I have
to reveal everything.

01:42:41.541 --> 01:42:46.375
For many years now,
Just to keep up the appearances…

01:42:47.375 --> 01:42:50.625
Everything in this house
is mortgaged to Amirchand.

01:42:51.375 --> 01:42:54.166
He has not even
spared this house.

01:42:56.500 --> 01:43:03.083
And he’s not even wavered While
stabbing his friend in the back.

01:43:03.916 --> 01:43:05.458
This traitor!

01:43:06.166 --> 01:43:15.625
Look,
Asutosh… There’s no friendship in business.

01:43:16.458 --> 01:43:18.666
-Give me my money back.

01:43:18.791 --> 01:43:24.833
-Hear me out, Amirchand. How will I arrange
for so much money At such short notice?

01:43:25.250 --> 01:43:26.625
-Please give me some more time.

01:43:27.416 --> 01:43:30.875
-How much more, Asutosh?

01:43:31.208 --> 01:43:38.000
If you can’t repay the loan,
Mortgage something else.

01:43:40.875 --> 01:43:48.375
How about the nose
ring on Goddess Laxmi?

01:43:49.375 --> 01:43:50.458
You can give me that.

01:43:52.500 --> 01:43:54.166
It’s an important
family heirloom.

01:43:55.250 --> 01:43:57.375
Forget family history…

01:43:59.416 --> 01:44:01.083
Don’t forget you’re in debt.

01:44:01.083 --> 01:44:03.291
You have no respect.

01:44:07.166 --> 01:44:07.916
Hello.

01:44:10.291 --> 01:44:12.750
Tell me Somnath.

01:44:13.000 --> 01:44:15.208
Yeah, we can talk.

01:44:16.375 --> 01:44:22.500
What? Listen to me…
Listen to me carefully.

01:44:22.958 --> 01:44:26.833
Everyone will not
know it’s value.

01:44:27.541 --> 01:44:29.083
Don’t tell anyone else about it.

01:44:30.666 --> 01:44:31.958
Keep the object with you.

01:44:32.666 --> 01:44:34.000
Where have you hidden it?

01:44:37.166 --> 01:44:38.375
You’ve sent me a letter?

01:44:39.916 --> 01:44:42.333
Okay, I’ll let you know… Okay.

01:44:49.000 --> 01:44:52.541
Hello,
Harinath. This is Somnath.

01:44:53.000 --> 01:44:56.250
Did Gobindo Ram
install the lock?

01:44:57.708 --> 01:44:59.458
That’s a relief!

01:45:01.041 --> 01:45:05.750
Harinath,
I’ve sent you a letter…

